# AWS Research Wizard

AWS Research Wizard provides comprehensive tools for configuring, deploying, and monitoring optimized AWS research environments across multiple scientific domains.

## Key Features

- **Interactive Domain Configuration**: 18+ pre-configured research packs including genomics, climate modeling, machine learning, and more
- **Infrastructure Deployment**: CloudFormation automation with EC2 instance provisioning and security group configuration  
- **Real-time Monitoring**: Live metrics, cost tracking, and alert management through interactive terminal dashboards
- **Single Binary Distribution**: Zero dependencies, cross-platform support
- **Cost Optimization**: Spot instance recommendations and real-time cost analysis

## Perfect For

- Research computing environments
- HPC workload deployment  
- Scientific computing on AWS
- Cost-optimized research infrastructure

## Quick Start

After installation, configure AWS credentials and start with:

```
aws-research-wizard config                   # Interactive domain configuration
aws-research-wizard deploy --domain genomics # Deploy a genomics environment
aws-research-wizard monitor                  # Launch monitoring dashboard
```

## Requirements

- AWS CLI configured with valid credentials
- Windows 10+ (64-bit)

## Documentation

Full documentation and examples available at: https://github.com/aws-research-wizard/aws-research-wizard
